<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/19979523-s-vasundara"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1387535201i/19979523._UX100_CR0,20,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/19979523-s-vasundara">S.vasundara</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">it basically about a girl who was kidnapped and then one day turned up lying in a stream next to her village (it set in a pretty old time) and its abo<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">it basically about a girl who was kidnapped and then one day turned up lying in a stream next to her village (it set in a pretty old time) and its about the life she leads now, having never recovered from what happened and still suffering its consequences, its a really nice read and yes it sounds very depressing but its actually not that bad.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
