        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer702497646" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15533232199458794012"><b>4.5 stars</b> There are about 100 reasons why this book wouldn&apos;t normally work for me. The story is related in fragments, often consisting of no more than half a page. The timeline is fluid, shifting between past and present. It&apos;s told in flipping SECOND PERSON NARRATIVE. But it works, it works beautifully. <br/><br/>Full review is on the blog: <a target='_blank' rel='noopener nofollow' href='http://www.themidnightgarden.net/2013/10/thissong.html'>http://www.themidnightgarden.net/2013...</a></span>
