          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer665278300" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9632808976730892994"><b>3.5 Stars</b><br/><br/>Hmm, this was an interesting one. It really wasn&apos;t what I was expecting, so that was cool. The style of it was unique and engaging––although the super-short chapters and use of second person were sometimes a bit irritating, I thought they still worked most of the time. I found the characters a little lacking and the end felt rushed to me (and maybe not very realistic, either). But over all I thought it was a memorable and intriguing book, and different from anything I&apos;ve read in a while</span>
  <span id="freeText9632808976730892994" style="display:none"><b>3.5 Stars</b><br /><br />Hmm, this was an interesting one. It really wasn't what I was expecting, so that was cool. The style of it was unique and engaging––although the super-short chapters and use of second person were sometimes a bit irritating, I thought they still worked most of the time. I found the characters a little lacking and the end felt rushed to me (and maybe not very realistic, either). But over all I thought it was a memorable and intriguing book, and different from anything I've read in a while.<br /><br />Longer review coming eventually!</span>
