        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1024134812" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4379937118508300094">A solid story, likeable characters, and a good theme. It was good. It wasn&apos;t, however, outstanding, or particularly original. That&apos;s the thing about a 3-star read. For me it means that I did like it, that maybe I didn&apos;t even have that many problems with it, but that overall, when everything is taken into account, I don&apos;t have much to say.<br/><br/>I actually read the majority of this in one sitting - it&apos;s interesting, for sure, but it didn&apos;t inspire me to run out ant talk about it. Honestly I&apos;m dragging t</span>
  <span id="freeText4379937118508300094" style="display:none">A solid story, likeable characters, and a good theme. It was good. It wasn't, however, outstanding, or particularly original. That's the thing about a 3-star read. For me it means that I did like it, that maybe I didn't even have that many problems with it, but that overall, when everything is taken into account, I don't have much to say.<br /><br />I actually read the majority of this in one sitting - it's interesting, for sure, but it didn't inspire me to run out ant talk about it. Honestly I'm dragging this review out trying to think of something valuable to say!</span>
